description: UeMC: Table containing User Equipment Mobility Connection (UeMC) information for each cell, including timestamp, location, cell identifiers, and mobility-related attributes.  dateTime: Timestamp of UeMC record; Area_Name: Name of the area (e.g., cell sector); CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Unclear identifier; vsDataType: Type of data (UeMC); vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; UeMC.userLabel: User label (appears unused); UeMC.ueMCId: Unique UeMC identifier; UeMC.freqSelAtBlindRwrToEutran: Frequency selection at blind handover to E-UTRAN.
